               <code code="44425-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="STORAGE AND HANDLING SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Store at controlled room temperature 59°-86°F (15°-30°C). Do not use on people with known allergies to benzocaine and PABA compounds.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20150430"/>
            </section>
